Text:
I have just tested both the "Update 4" and "Update 5" from Reloaded, and I can't get any of them to work with SKSE. I did a fresh install of Razor1911's Skyrim copy, and installed the update on top of this. But I still get "Please update to the latest version of Skyrim" when using skse_loader.exe. 

Has anyone gotten this update to work with any versions of SKSE?
